Welcome to @IrisUpdateBot!
The automatic social-media update bot, made by @themulti0

Here are the list of commands available:

/settings - Manage settings for connected chat

/subscriptions - Jump straight ahead to managing specifically platform subscriptions (possible to enter from /settings)

/language - Jump straight ahead to changing the interface's language (possible to enter from /settings)

/connect - Connect to a specific chat

/connection - Display current connected chat

/disconnect - Disconnect from connected chat, connect back to this DM chat
